{"tid":2135032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿列沙巴拿加撲救成功率53.5% 五大聯賽上陣25次或以上最低","createTime":"2020-08-01T06:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T13:29:19.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"faa762a29384faa381d8320eef61f14116730135","tid":2135032,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"Premier League<br />\n7月23日 &middot; <br />\n本賽季<br />\n五大聯賽上陣25次或以上<br />\n撲救成功率最低門將😬<br />\n<br />\n阿列沙巴拿加&mdash;53.5%<br />\n#PL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/113242770_4105124806224851_4637141254362718972_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Ssj57VKyGxIAX9Cm4XH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=62dd4a066058c89c2e03898abb36c3c6&amp;oe=5F4ACC4C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F113242770_4105124806224851_4637141254362718972_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DSsj57VKyGxIAX9Cm4XH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D62dd4a066058c89c2e03898abb36c3c6%26oe%3D5F4ACC4C&h=702d3057&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"277a76b225d8d7af3d959a16ad1c7fac93a40cf7","tid":2135032,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Pg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=657dbbbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\nKepa無聲告別唔會再為車路士披甲<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p640x640/116062330_3277488032329425_2623342353775134247_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=8zg3Hqmy-dEAX-EChtE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=c63a300e3263e50f071c0dc1c88bc5e6&amp;oe=5F4C9A15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp640x640%2F116062330_3277488032329425_2623342353775134247_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D8zg3Hqmy-dEAX-EChtE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Dc63a300e3263e50f071c0dc1c88bc5e6%26oe%3D5F4C9A15&h=751772c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車路士喺2018年以破龍門轉會費世界紀錄嘅7,200萬鎊，收購西班牙年輕門將阿列沙巴拿加(Kepa)，不過2年時間證明呢次買人係完全失敗，據報周六(8月1日)英足盃決賽，車仔領隊林柏特已決定用韋利卡巴尼路把關，而阿列沙巴拿加亦將會被賣走，意味呢位西班牙門將已踢完車路士最後一仗。<br />\n阿列沙巴拿加上季加盟後表現唔算太差，但今季就愈踢愈頹，撲救成功率係英超最差，踢41場比賽只有10場唔失波，季中一度被林柏特雪藏。<br />\n不過韋利卡巴尼路畢竟年紀大，上陣亦有犯錯，Kepa之後再拎番正選，但英超復賽後連場失誤，聯賽3比5慘敗利物浦後，林柏特再忍無可忍，煞科戰重新起用韋利卡巴尼路。<br />\n英國《太陽報》報道，林柏特決定英足盃決賽續用韋利卡巴尼路，如無意外之後歐聯都唔會再轉換正選，而且總監施治已經展開物色新門將行動，阿列沙巴拿加必定被賣走。對利物浦失5球，就係Kepa喺車路士告別戰。"},{"pid":"e6f6a66fbc9a2e87671436a57c6b104e81bb2218","tid":2135032,"uid":5649,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"80m買條傻西返黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皇馬果陣30m都唔買就知咩事啦"},{"pid":"db4ec9f4eee0ae5d178b2e9c12f4b10d9c1fd092","tid":2135032,"uid":9542,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"如果你識睇波，佢球球失親都係世界波黎，世界波救到就唔叫世界波，所以呢個數據反映唔到佢真正表現"},{"pid":"7428daae3a60e6b07ef355d1df3c460dd349d68e","tid":2135032,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e6f6a66fbc9a2e87671436a57c6b104e81bb2218","tid":2135032,"uid":5649,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"80m買條傻西返黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皇馬果陣30m都唔買就知咩事啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/116426199_3319146298124655_2765213773593924506_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Xm3-anP1cBoAX9xQkLv&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=db20233fcc676a3171e6c82c21add990&amp;oe=5F48F69D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F116426199_33191